data.description: Welcome to your future home in the charming heart of Daytona Beach! This beautifully remodeled 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers 1,496 square feet of elegant living space, tailored for modern comfort. The open and inviting floor plan showcases a designer kitchen with stunning granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, a chef's dream. Laminate flooring flows seamlessly throughout the home, providing both style and easy maintenance. The living room boasts a cozy fireplace, perfect for creating warm and memorable moments. Both bathrooms feature ceramic tile, offering a touch of sophistication to your daily routines. Significant updates include a new roof in 2022 and an A/C unit replacement in 2015. Outside, you'll discover a generous backyard for leisure and outdoor gatherings. This gem is located in a friendly neighborhood, just moments away from Daytona's renowned beaches, top-rated schools, shopping, and dining. Don't miss your chance to make this stunning property your own. Contact us now for an exclusive showing and seize this opportunity to call it home!
